synopsis: "The ocamlbuild build system (distributed with the compiler)"
description: """
Virtual package installed by OCaml compilers that included ocamlbuild.
ocamlbuild was moved out of the compiler distribution in OCaml 4.03.
"""
depends: "ocaml" {>= "3.10" & < "4.03"}
